{"tid":986432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【削長者綜援】補鑊措施須證無工作能力 邵家臻斥要老人自認廢老","createTime":"2019-01-18T12:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T09:31:46.000Z","uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3afc608d9cc8bdc3d5e2c82b10bba26f72d3bff4","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"【削長者綜援】補鑊措施須證無工作能力 邵家臻斥要老人自認廢老<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1061825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1061825&d=Ufld9kdgf6plUZmBe%2FWzNjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bc9e5f6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1061825&h=25830332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1061825</a><br />\n  <br />\n【削長者綜援】補鑊措施須證無工作能力 邵家臻斥要老人自認廢老 週五 2019-01-18 獨媒報導<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n（獨媒特約報導）政府於下月起將長者綜援申請年齡由60歲提高至65歲，引起各界不滿。行政長官林鄭月娥將會在中午宣佈新方案「補鑊」，有報導指60至64歲人士如果獲社工證明沒有工作能力，或長期尋找工作但失敗，將可獲得1,060元津貼，以填補長者綜援與成人綜援的差額。民主派立法會議員今早由立法會遊行到行政長官辦公室抗議，社福界邵家臻批評新方案造成標籤效應，「要老人家自認廢老，呢個係乜嘢政府？」<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻表示對於新方案失望及憤怒，又不滿政府昨日只和建制派議員見面討論新方案，沒有約見民主派。特首辦主任陳國基今早回覆邵家臻稱，林鄭昨日是會見行政會員成員及代表，邵家臻反駁代表根本不能出席機密會議。<br />\n<br />\n立法會昨日跨黨派通過檢討綜援計劃的無約束力議案，包括要求政府擱置將長者綜援申領年齡收緊至65歲。工黨張超雄強調，議案要求擱置方案，而不是「補鑊」，批評政策胡亂兼矛盾，「補鑊仲要俾行政費，社工上堂、手續費，乜都係錢。」"},{"pid":"486e1363a569d471ba33acf947f92712f6b87660","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"32d723e3e53cc8a3eefb0f115abaeef5f1483bff","tid":986432,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"關狗冇人理就心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb275b3bf86abf65497282838c8365e676c71404","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1d27d93985f0ef9614aad0ce01351e111161bd1a","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"f9e45eb54eddd8c3d363d644c75c653ea2739f3e","tid":986432,"uid":81518,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cb4795f30b13dab59e79d74003995517e636da7","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"0503abc0e79cdd66ad9359f6024e89e5244e35d2","tid":986432,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢地係唔係廢老"},{"pid":"c708924fe59a142da96cb5e90c384675d5355892","tid":986432,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32d723e3e53cc8a3eefb0f115abaeef5f1483bff","tid":986432,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"關狗冇人理就心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你冚家剷嘅話全連登心涼</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cebc892039f899a75d370465ab3d3415720557","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"2a43e5f9c065a35373a0738951a5fdf509038da0","tid":986432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"."}]}